1
00:07:48,050 --> 00:07:49,302
All right, Hector...

2
00:07:50,428 --> 00:07:51,429
...is this--?

3
00:07:51,971 --> 00:07:53,139
Is this green?

4
00:07:55,433 --> 00:07:56,767
Is this green?

5
00:08:00,813 --> 00:08:01,814
Excellent, Hector!

6
00:08:05,318 --> 00:08:08,070
Is this person angry?

7
00:08:14,327 --> 00:08:16,245
Is this person happy?

8
00:08:19,165 --> 00:08:22,293
Very good! That was much faster.

9
00:08:29,842 --> 00:08:32,428
We'll get back to work in just a second.

10
00:08:45,441 --> 00:08:48,736
It's okay, Hector.
Just a muscle spasm.

11
00:09:11,551 --> 00:09:13,344
Good. Let's continue.

12
00:09:17,682 --> 00:09:19,225
Are you with me?

13
00:09:25,815 --> 00:09:27,233
Is this Paris?

14
00:22:19,755 --> 00:22:22,632
Do you know how long
it's going to take to fix that?

15
00:22:23,091 --> 00:22:26,344
Maybe you like living in this hole,
but we want to go home!

16
00:22:30,891 --> 00:22:33,435
You're not the big boss here.

17
00:22:44,571 --> 00:22:47,199
Boys! Cool it!

18
00:28:09,854 --> 00:28:12,816
Naps are for old farts like you.

19
00:28:14,025 --> 00:28:15,902
And his German...

20
00:28:18,738 --> 00:28:20,323
...sounds stupid.

